{"author":"Iso Tester","data":{"body":"Correction: the A+B+C fixes are in PR #67 (not #66). PR #66 (MERGED to main) = the primary container-RuntimeError fix (a5dec5f60). PR #67 (commit ec85e4cd5) = the two exposed-issue fixes + tool-call backstop. NOTE: until #67 merges, main has the agentic-tier restore WITHOUT the ticket-store pin, so review-plan on an epic returns INDETERMINATE (agentic tier runs but hits the .tickets-tracker errors). #67 closes that window."},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"COMMENT","timestamp":1782612034053326001,"uuid":"6e47dbc0-92fa-4c42-9cbc-28cf57992e07"}